short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple way to detect website icons.
short.zh_CN: 探测网站图标的简单方式。

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Click the extension button to detect current website's icons.

Support:
- Favicon
- Icon
- Apple Touch Icon
- msapplication-TileImage
- msapplication-config
- Web App Manifest
- Fluid Icon
- Mask Icon

Github: https://github.com/BlackGlory/favicon-detector
